data.description: NEW ROOF AND NEW HOT WATER HEATER INSTALLED BEFORE CLOSING! BEAUTIFUL HOME WITH IRRIGATION WELL AND PRIVATE ACCESS TO RAINBOW RIVER! This spacious 3 bedroom 2 bathroom split plan, concrete block home sits high and dry on an oversized .38 acre lot with lush landscaping and shade trees which add to the curb appeal. Upon entry you will notice the large Great Room with vaulted ceilings, offering plenty of space for seating and entertaining and is open to the Formal Dining Room. The nicely appointed kitchen has a solar light, breakfast bar, wood cabinets, granite countertops and stainless steel appliances! Other features include inside laundry room, enclosed back porch with sliding insulated windows and outside patio perfect for a fire pit or outdoor entertaining. Amenities include recently remodeled clubhouse with 2 restaurants , treed walking trail, community pool, private beach, fitness center, tennis courts, and private River access to go tubing or launch kayaks and paddle boards, pavilions, playground, and more right on the pristine Rainbow River. The community is open to all ages and the Annual fee for amenities is less than $300/year!
